import React from "react";
import {
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Typography,
  CardActions,
  Button,
  TextField,
  Grid,
} from "@mui/material";

export default function SignupCard() {
  return (
    <Card sx={{ minWidth: 275 }}>
      <CardContent>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Typography variant="h5" component="div">
              Signup Form
            </Typography>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="First Name"
              variant="outlined"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="Last Name"
              variant="outlined"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="Email"
              variant="outlined"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="Phone No."
              variant="outlined"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <TextField
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="Phone No."
              variant="outlined"
            />
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </CardContent>
      <CardActions>
        <Button size="small">Learn More</Button>
      </CardActions>
    </Card>
  );
}
